architecture | acme/client | Extract EabAcmeClient base; add ZeroSSLAcmeClient and SectigoAcmeClient; update make_client() factory
feature | acme/client | Add ZeroSSL (acme.zerossl.com) and Sectigo (acme.sectigo.com) CA support with EAB credential injection
test | tests/test_unit_acme | Add 9 unit tests: EAB class hierarchy, factory dispatch, credential injection for new CA providers
test | agent/nodes/planner | Add 12 validation tests for LLM hallucinated domain filtering in planner output
test | agent/graph | Add 10 checkpoint/interrupt/resume tests using LangGraph MemorySaver; cover thread isolation and state integrity
feature | agent/revocation_graph | Implement certificate revocation as independent subgraph: account setup → domain loop → revoke → reporter
feature | agent/nodes/revoker | Add revoker node: POST /revokeCert with reason code; RFC 8555 compliant
feature | agent/nodes/revocation_router | Add revocation_router node: domain picking and routing for revocation subgraph
feature | agent/state | Add 5 AgentState fields for revocation: targets, current domain, reason, revoked, failed
feature | main | Add --revoke-cert CLI command with optional --reason code (0=unspecified, 1=keyCompromise, 4=superseded, 5=cessation)
feature | acme/dns_challenge | Implement DNS-01 challenge: compute_dns_txt_value(), DnsProvider ABC, Cloudflare/Route53/GoogleCloudDNS providers
feature | agent/nodes/challenge | Add DNS-01 branch in challenge setup/cleanup; import dns provider factory at module level
feature | agent/nodes/order | Mode-aware challenge type selection: dns-01 vs http-01 based on HTTP_CHALLENGE_MODE
feature | agent/state | Add auth_domains and dns_txt_values List[str] fields to AcmeOrder for DNS-01 support
feature | config | Add DNS_CHALLENGE_MODE="dns" validator; add 10 DNS provider config fields; add validate_dns_config model_validator
test | tests/test_dns_challenge | Add 45 unit tests for DNS-01: value computation, all three providers, factory dispatch
memory | .history | Add append-only architectural intent log to project root
docs | doc/wiki | Session 1: WIKI_OPERATIONS domain features; SECURITY/RFC/CI_TEST metadata; improves feature discoverability
docs | doc/wiki | Session 2: FEATURE_MATRIX.md and CA_PROVIDERS.md; bidirectional links DNS-01/Revocation↔WIKI_OPERATIONS
docs | doc/wiki | Add analysis documents: WIKI_STRUCTURAL_ANALYSIS, WIKI_NAVIGATION_MAP, WIKI_QUICK_FIXES for future maintainers
docs | doc/logger | Mark logger implementation as production (not plan); document LoggerWithRunID singleton, design rationale, integration
docs | doc/mcp | Document undocumented generate_test_cert tool; add to tool list, retrieval keywords, notes on serialization
